<view class="container">
  <view class="title">创建房间</view>
  
  <view class="card">
    <view class="subtitle">房间号</view>
    <view class="room-id-display">
      <text class="room-id">{{roomId || '生成中...'}}</text>
    </view>
    <button class="btn btn-special" bindtap="copyRoomId" disabled="{{!roomId}}">
      复制房间号
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="subtitle">邀请好友</view>
    <view class="invite-text">
      分享房间号给朋友，让他们通过"加入房间"输入房间号即可加入游戏
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="btn" bindtap="enterWaitingRoom">进入等待室</button>
  <button class="btn btn-secondary" bindtap="backToHome">返回首页</button>
</view>